==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Suprarenal
<hw>Su`pra*re"nal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Anat.)</fld>
<def>Situated above, or anterior to, the kidneys.</def> --
<def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>A suprarenal capsule.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Suprarenal capsules</b></col> <fld>(Anat.)</fld>, <cd>two
small bodies of unknown function in front of, or near, the kidneys in
most vertebrates. Also called <altname>renal capsules</altname>, and
<altname>suprarenal bodies</altname>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Suprascalpulary</ent>⟦br⟧
<ent>Suprascalpular</ent>⟦br⟧
